gram\": \"the 400m\", \"from\": 247, \"to\": 255}, {\"ngram\": \"her Wednesday night\", \"from\": 282, \"to\": 301}, {\"ngram\": \"a time\", \"from\": 318, \"to\": 324}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Her time was the sixth fastest of the eight across the three semi-finals and she will be hoping for a big improvement to be in podium contention.\", \"from\": 336, \"to\": 481, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Her time\", \"from\": 336, \"to\": 344}, {\"ngram\": \"the three semi\", \"from\": 387, \"to\": 401}, {\"ngram\": \"finals\", \"from\": 402, \"to\": 408}, {\"ngram\": \"a big improvement\", \"from\": 436, \"to\": 453}, {\"ngram\": \"podium contention\", \"from\": 463, \"to\": 480}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Ireland will also be involved in two semi-finals on the track on Friday morning withMark Englishtargeting an 800m final at 10.30am andSarah Lavinin the 100m hurdles shortly after at 11.05am.\", \"from\": 483, \"to\": 673, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 483, \"end\": 490, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"score\": 0.9999998572263951, \"rank\": 1.4153064064057985e-07, \"text\": \"Ireland\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"two semi\", \"from\": 516, \"to\": 524}, {\"ngram\": \"finals\", \"from\": 525, \"to\": 531}, {\"ngram\": \"the track\", \"from\": 535, \"to\": 544}, {\"ngram\": \"Friday morning\", \"from\": 548, \"to\": 562}, {\"ngram\": \"an 800m\", \"from\": 589, \"to\": 596}, {\"ngram\": \"10.30am andSarah Lavinin\", \"from\": 606, \"to\": 630}, {\"ngram\": \"the 100m hurdles\", \"from\": 631, \"to\": 647}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Also on the track will beIreland's women's 4x400m team, who will take part in the second semi-final heat at 9.52am.\", \"from\": 675, \"to\": 790, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the track\", \"from\": 683, \"to\": 692}, {\"ngram\": \"part\", \"from\": 745, \"to\": 749}, {\"ngram\": \"the second semi-final heat\", \"from\": 753, \"to\": 779}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The four athletes chosen to compete in the semi-final areSophie Becker,Phil Healy,Kelly McGroryandSharlene Mawdsley.\", \"from\": 792, \"to\": 908, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 856, \"end\": 862, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Boris_Becker\", \"score\": 0.999851743953284, \"rank\": 0.00012395519742997222, \"text\": \"Becker\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Boris_Becker\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Boris_Becker\"}, {\"begin\": 863, \"end\": 873, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Phil_Healy\", \"score\": 0.9999865515186963, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Phil Healy\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Phil_Healy\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Phil_Healy\"}, {\"begin\": 874, \"end\": 879, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kelly_Osbourne\", \"score\": 0.999999994016207, \"rank\": 5.953743617599835e-09, \"text\": \"Kelly\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kelly_Osbourne\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kelly_Osbourne\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The four athletes\", \"from\": 792, \"to\": 809}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Kate O'Connorwill wrap up a busy day in the Stade de France for Team Ireland when she competes in the closing leg of the women's heptathlon.\", \"from\": 910, \"to\": 1050, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 910, \"end\": 914, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kate_Ramsay\", \"score\": 0.9972444570053535, \"rank\": 0.002762706769052032, \"text\": \"Kate\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kate_Ramsay\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kate_Ramsay\"}, {\"begin\": 974, \"end\": 986, \"title\": \"http://d